## Directions and parking

On street parking in either Inverness Rd, Manor Rd (BB3 2SN) or Belgrave Rd (BB3 2SF) surrounding the park. Please park on one side of the road only, to allow easy flow of local traffic.

From N, E and W exit the M65 at J4 and follow A666 in a southerly direction to Darwen centre. At the one way system, double back on yourself signed for Blackburn, but immediately bear 2nd left uphill on to Borough Rd, leading to the park.
From the S follow A666 north to Darwen centre. At the one way system, immediately bear 2nd left uphill on to Borough Rd.

